{"tid":678380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港眾志宣布轉型為民間政治團體","createTime":"2018-05-26T04:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T03:17:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc96c24af296accbb87a71c2a24bf486dde8520","tid":678380,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:41:43.000Z","msg":"香港眾志昨晚舉行黨慶，宣布轉型，不再以政黨自居，將轉型為民間政治團體，與民主陣營光譜各派保持合作。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志表示，過去一年經歷前主席羅冠聰被褫奪立法會議席，多名領軍人物相繼入獄，前常委周庭被取消參選資格，不同成員相繼被剝奪政治權利後，政黨的參選之路明顯已中斷，是時候反思出路。<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志表示，告別議會路線後，將專注民間社會，也表明會全面迎戰《基本法》廿三條。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E7%82%BA%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94-233343452.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E8%25BD%2589%25E5%259E%258B%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594-233343452.html&d=2aExcw5PoHOJBrg3cG3sSNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=598902fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E8%BD%89%E5%9E%8B%E7%82%BA%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94-233343452.html</a><br />\n<br />\n自動降呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c30543ec09820eb3605ca141c9c320a8456db19","tid":678380,"uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"下一步會轉型為壓力團體?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7422137b01949f3375db9594046d95a67633c769","tid":678380,"uid":43575,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"1c30543ec09820eb3605ca141c9c320a8456db19","tid":678380,"uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T04:42:59.000Z","msg":"下一步會轉型為壓力團體?<img src=\"/asset